claim.claim-text:
1. A method of including a jackpot component in a primary wagering game played by at least one player, comprising the steps of: 
a. requiring each player to place a wager on the primary wagering game; 
b. conducting a round of the primary wagering game with the players; 
c. designating as a winner each player having a predetermined arrangement of indicia resulting from completion of the round; and 
d. providing an opportunity for each winner to win a prize that is randomly chosen from a group of prizes that includes an incrementing jackpot.
